note as RULE
  **ANSWER_CORRECTION_RULE:**
  Human answers are **higher priority** than Git reconstruction.
  POC / prototype / rejected option / unfinished work
  in an answer -> narrative narrowed, not appended as caveat.
  Empty answer -> keep Git reconstruction for that part.
end note

note bottom of Q
  Questions are the **primary product** of the whole pipeline.
  final is where they get **answered** and become confirmed context.
end note

