@startuml final-qa-artifacts
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FAFAFA

title **Q&A artifact model** (§7, §11) — not stored in prepared/

left to right direction

package "**prepared/** (no answers)" #FFF3E0 {
  class "PreparedRecord" as PR {
    model.questionsAnalyses
    model.history
    no answers field
  }
}

package "**finish/** question files" #FCE4EC {
  class "FinishQuestionsRecord" as FQ1 {
    <<v1>>
    questions: id + question
  }
  class "FinishQuestionsRecord" as FQ2 {
    <<v2>>
    questions: id + question
  }
}

package "**finish/** archive" #E1F5FE {
  class "FinishRecord" as FR {
    sourceQuestions
    finishId -> v1, v2
    answers: questionId + answer
    version
  }
}

PR ..> FQ1 : final writes\nquestion text
PR ..> FQ2 : deepen / extension\nwrites new round

FQ1 <-- FR : v1 -> <id>.question.json
FQ2 <-- FR : v2 -> <id>.question.vN.json

note bottom of FR
  **prepare** reads prior Q&A by resolving
  answers[] against question files for all
  labels in sourceQuestions (latest finish).
  Re-running final reuses saved answers;
  prepared record stays clean.
end note

@enduml
